    "en": {
      "title": "Earthquake in China: 46 dead",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "A powerful 6.8-magnitude earthquake has struck China's mountainous Sichuan province.",
        "Following the earthquake in Sichuan province today (5), a second earthquake was felt in Yan city in the next 40 minutes. The earthquake measured 4.2 on the Richter scale.",
        "It is reported that 46 people have died and 16 people are missing due to this powerful earthquake in China."
      ],
